```
SELECT * FROM geoTest where  ST_DISTANCE(locationSTPoint, ST_Point(77.62357943770779, 12.933540687183736, 1)) < 500
```

Fails with exception without this fix since the mutable index has incorrect docIds in the h3Id -> bitmap mapping. In some cases, it's possible for the query to return incorrect documents too.
